Based on my thorough exploration of the shadcn/ui codebase, here's a comprehensive understanding of how the registry system works:

### Registry Files Location

**Primary Registry Definition Files:**
- `/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/registry.ts` - Main registry for base (root aggregator)
- `/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/_registry.ts` - UI component definitions
- `/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/examples/_registry.ts` - Example/demo definitions
- `/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/components/_registry.ts` - Complex components
- `/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/hooks/_registry.ts` - Custom hooks
