### Registry Item Types

The registry supports these types (from `registryItemTypeSchema`):

1. **`registry:ui`** - Single-file UI components/primitives
2. **`registry:block`** - Complex multi-file components
3. **`registry:component`** - Simple components
4. **`registry:hook`** - Custom React hooks
5. **`registry:lib`** - Utility functions and helpers
6. **`registry:page`** - Page or route files (requires `target`)
7. **`registry:file`** - Miscellaneous files (requires `target`)
8. **`registry:theme`** - Theme configuration
9. **`registry:style`** - Style/design system definitions
10. **`registry:base`** - Entire design system bases
11. **`registry:font`** - Font definitions (requires `font` metadata)
12. **`registry:example`** - Demo/example components (internal)

