```

**Associated Example Entry:**
```typescript
{
  name: "dropdown-menu-example",
  title: "Dropdown Menu",
  type: "registry:example",
  registryDependencies: [
    "avatar",
    "button",
    "dropdown-menu",
    "checkbox",
    "dialog",
    "input",
